===Noun===
'''truth''' (''plural:'' [[truths]])

# That which is [[true]].
# That which conforms to [[reality]].
# Telling it like it is.
# The degree of correspondence between a representation and what is being represented.
# What we understand, of the pursuit of understanding more of all the senses of feelings of our individual lives.

